WEBVTT

00:05.967 --> 00:07.233
Previously on <i>Royal Pains...</i>

00:07.235 --> 00:08.401
Wanna go fishing tomorrow morning?

00:08.403 --> 00:09.502
Didn't you just say
you have an appointment

00:09.504 --> 00:10.703
with Dr. Greene tomorrow morning?

00:10.705 --> 00:11.438
He never came in for the procedure.

00:11.440 --> 00:12.439
What?

00:12.441 --> 00:14.474
- How's Jack?
- Not so hot.

00:14.476 --> 00:16.576
I had him rest
while we head back to shore.

00:16.578 --> 00:18.578
I have a fully fleshed out business plan.

00:18.580 --> 00:20.647
I know that's your plan.

00:20.649 --> 00:22.082
But what if it's not my plan?

00:22.084 --> 00:23.716
It's my job to grow the business.

00:23.718 --> 00:24.918
Not this business.

00:24.920 --> 00:26.319
Not this way.

00:26.321 --> 00:28.388
I purposefully kept the family
away from this event, Claudette,

00:28.390 --> 00:29.789
so what are you doing here?

00:29.791 --> 00:31.324
The Rateniczes thought that a christening

00:31.326 --> 00:33.927
was the ideal place
to extend an olive branch.

00:33.929 --> 00:35.261
Your parents cut you off,

00:35.263 --> 00:37.197
and his parents stuck you
with the wedding bill.

00:37.199 --> 00:38.965
It's not right. Here's my pitch,

00:38.967 --> 00:40.533
I buy your 1/3 stake in Hankmed.

00:40.535 --> 00:41.768
- Evan...
- The moment you can

00:41.770 --> 00:43.236
buy it back, it's yours again.

00:43.238 --> 00:47.006
Sure there are more than
enough medical professionals

00:47.008 --> 00:48.875
to keep an eye on me overnight.

00:48.877 --> 00:52.645
I'm not staying as your doctor.

00:52.647 --> 00:54.080
I'm staying as your friend.

00:56.717 --> 00:59.452
We lost him.

00:59.454 --> 01:01.521
Jack's dead.

